Current Structure (Key Components)

- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/adapters/csv_adapter.py`: Adapter for parsing CSV course data.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/adapters/pdf.py`: Adapter for parsing PDF content into text items.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/adapters/pptx.py`: Adapter for parsing PowerPoint slides.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/adapters/txt.py`: Adapter for parsing plain text files.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/aligner.py`: TranscriptAligner to align slides ↔ transcripts.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/anki_bridge.py`: AnkiConnect bridge (add/update/delete/move cards).
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/config/courses.json`: Course list/config used by server.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/entities.py`: EntityDetector and predicate extraction.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/manifest.yaml`: Manifest mapping course materials to modules and files.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/manifest_loader.py`: Loads and resolves manifest file paths.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/ngrok.yml`: ngrok config for stable domain tunneling to local 8000.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/server.py`: Main FastMCP server; tools: modules, ingest, search, export, Anki deck ops.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/START_DRCODEPT.bat`: Startup script: activates venv and runs Uvicorn on 127.0.0.1:8000.
- `PROGRAMS/fastmcp-server/verifier.py`: Two-source verification of extracted facts.
